document_data.name: Eleriel Obarskyr
document_data.mainbody: '''Eleriel Obarskyr''' was queen of [[Cormyr]] through marriage to [[Anglond Obarskyr]].
document_data.Relatives: Eleriel was married to King [[Anglond Obarskyr]]. Their only son would become King [[Azoun I]].
